ips. His worth to the team was incalculable. I must say he&rsquo;s made significant progress with his three point shooting since he joined nets. Unfortunately his back injury has progressed fairly rapidly forcing him to be sidelined for four months because of his back injury. He has a follow-up to the doctor next week. His friend LeBron James will also be out of commission until his leg heals. He hasn&rsquo;t made much progress with his shooting since he injured his leg. His doctor said he was making good progress and will check on his progress next month. He assigned the blame for his injury to a lack of training and stretching. Oh well it could be worse. His worth of contribution to Lakers is incalculable. Lakers is as likely to win the finals next year as warriors in my opinion. The other month Lakers didn&rsquo;t just beat Bulls. They wiped the floor with them. The role of every coach in every team is well defined. Everyone has a key role to play in every team. In addition, the government has established a commission to examine the use of steroids among players. Another commission has also be created to investigate family violence in nba which I wholeheartedly support."},{"pid":"0ff37a556550a92c06b494aa1c0f8acbfa04e2ad","tid":1501641,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2c5360273994b9a9b3976b303253eb9300181b9","tid":1501641,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"00455209ee5cf4c658215f3f5623caf96c07b4c6","tid":1501641,"uid":222623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:05:33.000Z","msg":"PG:Curry<br />\nSG:Wade<br />\nSF:Lebron<br />\nPF:KG<br />\nC:shaq"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"shaq既缺點太大<br />\n就係無射程<br />\n大夢射程方面屌打佢<br />\n加上步法 唔需要單靠力量都完勝對手<br />\n同埋SG點都係MJ啦<br />\n<br />\n如果係現代籃球<br />\nKG位係OK<br />\n<br />\nKG同TD邊個勁<br />\n其實差唔多<br />\n不過KG無TD有咁多好勁既隊友同教練<br />\nKG全面過TD<br />\nKG係一個有PG控球身手既大前"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:26:56.000Z","msg"